    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"ultimate release\"... that's a heavy way to put it. it kind of makes it sound like the erasure isn't even a bad thing, more like a relief. like, instead of fighting to stay \"real\" in a world that's rejecting them, they could just... stop. do you really think it's better for them to just give up and let it happen?",
